{"type": "article", "id": 9676, "title": "SLOWood 香插", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-18T07:23:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235644itaKfQ4GwsDFznvk.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t一眼望过去，你大概很难看出来这个小山模样的物件是什么用途。这是一款来自北京 SLOWood 工作室的香插，远山的造型取材自传统水墨画的技法和习惯，和“香”——这种中国传统物品相得益彰，尤其是当烟雾氤氲，看起来就像是两座静谧的小山。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235641tn1EqpxdiZyIMDw9.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235642QlJngCTkBos6fj8R.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.65208333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235642yAaoJHNnYRVTm9Sb.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.74166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235643QVhMAm0sUzbfvlte.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.67083333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235643xQz98EihAVumWtH3.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.72708333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}